# Keep repo-root docker build contexts small and cache-stable. Two builds use
# this context: deploy/runtime/Dockerfile (needs go.mod/go.sum, cmd/, internal/,
# vendor-martian/) and test/e2e/docker_iso.sh's heredoc image (additionally
# needs the built ./mre and testdata/) — so only genuinely unused trees are
# excluded here.
.git
.github
.claude
artifacts
deploy/awsbatch-cdk/node_modules
deploy/awsbatch-cdk/cdk.out
out-*
work
results
.nextflow*
